# NYRA - Neural Yielding Resilient Assistant

Production-ready AI application with Gemini Nano + Gemini Pro hybrid architecture.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Configure environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API keys

# Run application
python backend/app.py
```

Visit: http://localhost:5000

## Features

- 6 AI Tools: Prompt, Summarizer, Translator, Writer, Proofreader, Rewriter
- SQL Optimizer with BigQuery integration
- DevOps Analyzer for infrastructure code
- Prompt Chain Builder
- Real-time Analytics Dashboard
- Multi-Agent AI System
- Hybrid AI (On-Device + Cloud)
- Firebase Authentication
- Offline Capable

## Tech Stack

- Backend: Python/Flask
- Frontend: HTML5/CSS3/JavaScript
- AI: Gemini Nano + Gemini Pro
- Database: Firebase Firestore
- Analytics: BigQuery
- Cloud: Google Cloud Platform

## API Endpoints

All endpoints return JSON and handle errors gracefully.

### Chrome AI APIs
- POST /api/chrome-ai/prompt
- POST /api/chrome-ai/summarize
- POST /api/chrome-ai/translate
- POST /api/chrome-ai/write
- POST /api/chrome-ai/proofread
- POST /api/chrome-ai/rewrite

### Gemini Pro APIs
- POST /api/gemini/generate
- POST /api/gemini/analyze-devops
- POST /api/gemini/multi-agent

### BigQuery APIs
- POST /api/bigquery/optimize
- GET /api/bigquery/analytics

### Firebase APIs
- POST /api/firebase/auth/verify
- POST /api/firebase/data/save
- POST /api/firebase/data/get

